title: What's Ahead For Mortgage Rates
itunes:title: What's Ahead For Mortgage Rates
description:
Katherine Hawkins, Portfolio Manager and SVP at Vertical Capital Income Fund (NYSE:VCIF), discusses the mortgage market and investing. Anders Persson, CIO at Nuveen, talks markets, and wraps up the Jackson Hole meeting. Priya Misra, Managing Director and Global Head of Rates Strategy at TD Securities, talks Jackson Hole, and gives her market outlook. Sonali Basak, Bloomberg Wall Street reporter, discusses the latest Wall Street news. Hosted by Paul Sweeney and Matt Miller.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
